6z\"></path></svg></a>Dependencies</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"table.md\">Table</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"properties\"><a href=\"#properties\" aria-label=\"properties permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Properties</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Type</th>\n<th>Default</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>columnWidths?</td>\n<td>Array&#x3C;<a href=\"#tablecolumnwidthinfo\">TableColumnWidthInfo</a>></td>\n<td></td>\n<td>Specifies column widths.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>minColumnWidth?</td>\n<td>number</td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">45</code> for <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@devexpress/dx-react-grid-bootstrap3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bootstrap3</a>; <code class=\"language-text\">55</code> for <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@devexpress/dx-react-grid-bootstrap4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bootstrap4</a>; <code class=\"language-text\">40</code> for <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@devexpress/dx-react-grid-material-ui\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Material-UI</a>;</td>\n<td>Specifies a column's minimum width.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>maxColumnWidth?</td>\n<td>number</td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">Infinity</code></td>\n<td>Specifies a column's maximum width.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>defaultColumnWidths?</td>\n<td>Array&#x3C;<a href=\"#tablecolumnwidthinfo\">TableColumnWidthInfo</a>></td>\n<td>[]</td>\n<td>Specifies initial column widths in uncontrolled